manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "dex-data-realtime-rs"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "dex-data-realtime-rs"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
anchor-lang = "0.27.0"
anyhow = "1.0"
arrayref = "0.3.6"
async-trait = "0.1"
borsh = "0.9"
bs58 = "0.5.0"
cron = "0.12"
dotenv = "0.15"
futures = "0.3.28"
num-traits = "0.2"
num_enum = "0.6.1"
openbook_dex = "0.5.6"
postgrest = "1.6.0"
serde = "1"
serde_derive = "1"
serde_json = "1"
solana-account-decoder = "1.17.6"
solana-client = "1.17.6"
solana-sdk = "1.17.6"
tracing = "0.1.37"
tracing-subscriber = "0.3.17"

[dependencies.bytemuck]
version = "1.4.0"

[dependencies.futures-util]
version = "0.3.28"
features = ["sink", "std"]
default-features = false

[dependencies.redis]
version = "0.23.3"
features = ["tokio-comp"]

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.11.22"
features = ["json", "serde_json", "native-tls"]

[dependencies.sqlx]
version = "0.6"
features = ["runtime-tokio-native-tls", "postgres", "chrono", "decimal", "offline"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.yellowstone-grpc-client]
git = "https://github.com/rpcpool/yellowstone-grpc.git"

[dependencies.yellowstone-grpc-proto]
git = "https://github.com/rpcpool/yellowstone-grpc.git"
